# Amazon & eBay seller login only blocklist for Surge
# Front-safe version: does NOT block normal shopping/front pages such as www.amazon.* or www.ebay.*
# Generated: 2026-06-25
# Recommended policy: REJECT
# Usage in Surge [Rule]:
# RULE-SET,https://your-host/amazon-ebay-login-only-front-safe.surge.list,REJECT

# ============================================================
# Amazon Seller Central login / seller backend domains
# These do not block Amazon shopping front pages.
# ============================================================
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.com
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.ca
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.com.mx
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.com.br
DOMAIN,sellercentral-europe.amazon.com
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.ie
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.com.be
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.nl
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.se
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.pl
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.co.za
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.eg
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.com.tr
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.sa
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.ae
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.in
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.sg
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.co.jp
DOMAIN,sellercentral.amazon.com.au

# Amazon seller recruiting / seller registration pages
# These are seller-facing pages, not shopping front pages.
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.com
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.ca
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.com.mx
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.com.br
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.co.uk
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.de
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.fr
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.it
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.es
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.nl
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.se
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.pl
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.com.tr
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.sa
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.ae
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.in
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.sg
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.co.jp
DOMAIN,sell.amazon.com.au

# ============================================================
# eBay login domains
# These avoid blocking www.ebay.* product/front pages.
# Note: blocking signin.ebay.* also blocks normal buyer account login on eBay,
# but browsing/listing pages remain accessible.
# ============================================================
